Meanwhile, the <span style="color: #fe9e00;">**ASPD**</span> is essentially dead, having secured a negligible [+ aspd_saxony_elections_vote +]% of the vote. While discussions of a merger with the Saxon <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> have emerged, but our party's leftist tilt has so far stalled any meaningful progress.

